"MSVC 19.15 (Visual Studio 2017 version 15.8) and later. (#GH47114)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:797
msgid ""
"``-fmacro-prefix-map=`` (``-ffile-prefix-map=``) now affects an anonymous "
"namespace hash generation for the MSVC targets and allows deterministic "
"symbol mangling for reproducible builds."
msgstr ""

