#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:825
msgid ""
"The driver default for the linker flag `-bcdtors` now defaults to `mbr` "
"(instead of `all`) which only extracts static init from archive members "
"which would otherwise be referenced. (See https://www.ibm.com/docs/en/"
"aix/7.2.0?topic=l-ld-command for details)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:829
msgid ""
"The driver now uses ``-lcompiler_rt`` instead of ``-latomic``, and the "
"compiler-rt archive has been renamed from ``libatomic.a`` to "
"``libcompiler_rt.a`` to avoid conflicts between the LLVM libatomic and the "
"GNU libatomic from the AIX toolbox as they share the same library name."
msgstr ""

