msgstr ""

#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:868
msgid "clang-format"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:869
msgid ""
"Add ``ObjCSpaceAfterMethodDeclarationPrefix`` option to control space "
"between the '-'/'+' and the return type in Objective-C method declarations"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:871
msgid ""
"Deprecate the ``BinPackParameters`` and ``BinPackArguments`` options and "
"replace them with the ``PackParameters`` and ``PackArguments`` structs "
"(respectively) to unify packing behavior. Add the ``BreakAfter`` option to "
"the structs, allowing parameter and argument lists to be formatted with one "
"parameter/argument on each line if they exceed the specified count."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:876
msgid ""
"Add ``AfterComma`` value to ``BreakConstructorInitializers`` to allow "
"breaking constructor initializers after commas, keeping the colon on the "
"same line."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:878
msgid ""
"Extend ``BreakBinaryOperations`` to accept a structured configuration with "
"per-operator break rules and minimum chain length gating via ``PerOperator``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:880
msgid ""
"Add ``AllowShortRecordOnASingleLine`` option and set it to "
"``EmptyAndAttached`` for LLVM style."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:881
msgid ""
"Add ``BreakFunctionDeclarationParameters`` option to always break before "
"function declaration parameters."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:883
msgid ""
"Add ``EnumAssignments`` option to ``AlignConsecutiveAssignments`` for "
"aligning enum assignments without affecting other assignments."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ReleaseNotes.rst:885
msgid ""
"Add ``BreakBeforeReturnType`` option to break before the function return "
"type."
msgstr ""

